{"tid":1134654,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解足球啲highlight片質素咁差？？","createTime":"2019-05-01T22:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T22:43:09.000Z","uid":132227,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8bef137a36120121a3e97fcd21f1f76f0320a920","tid":1134654,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:38:27.000Z","msg":"小妹好少睇波 （男友睇我對波多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n但有時見到啲討論得勁既比賽都會想睇下highlight<br />\n法國搵親既質素都好差<br />\n唔係統一channel同唔係英文都算數<br />\n條條片啲畫質都好差 有720p已經要拜神<br />\n仲要有時睇睇下冇撚咗後邊幾個入波<br />\ncut片又cut到冇前冇後<br />\n完全睇唔到啲攻勢點黎<br />\n未解晒圍又cut走埋<br />\n入波想睇多幾個replay或者慢鏡都少<br />\n<br />\n足球依啲咁多人睇既運動點解啲highlight片質素都咁差？<br />\nnba依啲細蚊仔玩既玩具highlight片又咁清咁好<br />\n我已經係去youtube睇最多view數嗰啲<br />\n係咪有咩秘密地方有好啲既highlight我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ed9e42254eb4f8d0f7b2da03308bd68331db07","tid":1134654,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:41:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7a3bee39d1b463dc7cac81cf3633a8e37e0d49f","tid":1134654,"uid":30615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:41:09.000Z","msg":"版權問題"},{"pid":"d3adcb32e618912ddb7d7f99ec5e71e90990b6a3","tid":1134654,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04ed9e42254eb4f8d0f7b2da03308bd68331db07","tid":1134654,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:41:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T22:43:09.000Z","msg":"好似唔係好齊 想睇頭先痢對疤都冇"}]}